    "body": "See e1bbdc2bfc2df24f04cfdbdfa13a46788d5ea40c for the general idea. The reason behind this is that I like to setup a certain set of routes to happen before general middleware like session, cookie, etc. This allows me to group those types of routes into something easily exportable from files/modules to be included in the main 'app'\n",
